{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8ee09e7c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s290i–3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"290i–3"},"text":"§ 290i–3.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Applicability of Bretton Woods Agreements Act","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The provisions of section 4 of the Bretton Woods Agreements Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s286b"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 286b","children":[],"tail":") shall apply with respect to the Bank to the same extent as with respect to the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Monetary Fund."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8ee09e7d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/35/tXIII/s1335"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–35, title XIII, § 1335","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/741"},"text":"95 Stat. 741","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/240/tV/s541/e/7"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–240, title V, § 541(e)(7)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/2519"},"text":"103 Stat. 2519","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8ee09e7e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8ee09e7f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id8ee09e80-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Bretton Woods Agreements Act, referred to in section catchline, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1945-07-31/ch339"},"text":"act July 31, 1945, ch. 339","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/59/512"},"text":"59 Stat. 512","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to subchapter XV (§ 286 et seq.) of this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s286"},"text":"section 286 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id8ee09e81-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1989—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/240"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–240","children":[],"tail":" struck out at end “Reports with respect to the Bank under paragraphs (5) and (6) of section 4 of that Act shall be included in the first and subsequent reports made thereunder after the United States accepts membership in the Bank.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
